dct_title_s: Sketch map of Mr. Baines' routes between the Limpopo and Zambesi rivers
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Territories of major indigenous groups and Transvaal Republic shown by color shading. Includes dates of travel and information on terrain, vegetation, and geology along Mr. Baines's route. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 41 (1871), pp. 100-31; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, [1871].
